```

% Important

- Follow PDD conventions: prompts define WHAT, not HOW
- Requirements should be testable and behavioral
- Keep prompts at 10-30% of expected code size
- Consider backward compatibility
- If no prompt changes are needed, report `No Changes Required` and proceed to Step 9; do not emit `STOP_CONDITION` for this case
- Always include exactly one `<step_report>...</step_report>` block before completing
